1
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:13,600
It's you.

2
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:19,440
Song Huainan.

3
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,800
I’ve been living in shame and hiding all these years.

4
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,400
I didn't expect you to come.

5
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:27,480
Why did you show up then?

6
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:31,760
You must have met Qingzhou.

7
00:00:32,159 --> 00:00:34,620
It seems that he is against me behind my back.

8
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,360
It's all because of you, bitch!

9
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:39,720
to go against you.

10
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,920
Song Huainan, you are a bad guy.

11
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:44,120
There are so many people

12
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:45,920
who want to kill them.

13
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:49,280
Stop talking nonsense.

14
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:49,920
Tell me.

15
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:52,000
Do you know Zhu Luolli?

16
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:54,120
Did she tell you

17
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,800
in your store?

18
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,040
Tell me.

19
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:59,480
I don't know what you're talking about.

20
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:02,880
I don't know Zhu Luoli.

21
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,960
This is just an ordinary soap.

22
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,520
Tell me, where is Zhu Luolli?

23
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:13,880
I don't know him.

24
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,600
I don't know you even if you kill me.

25
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,000
Don't be ungrateful.

26
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:20,200
I wanted to spare your life.

27
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,960
I asked her to disappear, not to let her die.

28
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:27,560
Commander, please forgive me this time.

29
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:29,960
Fine.

30
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,160
Shoot me if you dare.

31
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,240
Song Huainan.

32
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,200
Don’t think you can cover the world.

33
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,360
I'm telling you, you'll be punished.

34
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:40,320
You're just like your son.

35
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:38,840
Search.

36
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,079
Yes.

37
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,720
Mother.

38
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,560
Mother!

39
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:50,720
Mother!

40
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:51,880
Mother!

41
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,880
Mother!

42
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,640
My boat.

43
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:08,280
This is your favorite egg noodles when you were young.

44
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:11,360
You're my only child.

45
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:15,240
How can I put you in trouble for me?

46
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,200
Song Huainan, you bastard!

47
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,040
What?

48
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,440
Do you want to die too?

49
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,820
Do you want me to walk you down?

50
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,280
and accompany your mother?

51
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,240
Song Huainan.

52
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,360
Why did you kill my mother?

53
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,920
Are you going to kill them all?

54
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:02,320
I gave her a chance, but she doesn't cherish it.

55
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,320
She insisted on going against me.

56
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,320
You want to die?

57
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,680
I'm the one who's against you.

58
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,640
Come at me if you have anything.

59
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,280
Why did you kill my mother?

60
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,600
Why?

61
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:15,360
For the sake of our family, I'm standing firmly in Jiangcheng.

62
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,680
so that you can rest assured

63
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,200
and be the second young master of the Song family.

64
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,680
Why?

65
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,079
I was going to ask you.

66
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,600
Why are you doing this to me again and again?

67
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,440
Do you think I'm your brother?

68
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,960
You colluded with the Westerners and sold your country for glory.

69
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:30,680
You killed countless people for your money and status.

70
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,340
You said you did everything for the Song family.

71
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,640
If that's the case,

72
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,370
I would rather not have a brother like you.

73
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:50,360
Song Qingzhou, this is the last time.

74
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,680
If it happens again,

75
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:54,480
don't blame me for disregarding our brotherhood.

76
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:02,080
Song Huainan.

77
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,520
Tell me.

78
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,480
How's the investigation going?

79
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,040
It's all been investigated.

80
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,560
When the Yao family launched the sample,

81
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,690
Madam was there too.

82
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,680
According to the workers' memory,

83
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,120
Madam put something

84
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,200
in the sample.

85
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,680
But he didn't see it clearly.

86
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,800
It's her.

87
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,360
Tell them to send all the information

88
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,400
to me.

89
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,440
Yao Sheng.

90
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,320
Aunt Hong.

91
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:10,880
Aunt Hong.

92
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,240
Luo Li.

93
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,010
I lost my mother.

94
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,280
It's my fault for getting Aunt Hong involved.

95
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,159
It's my fault.

96
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,040
for not protecting my mother.

97
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,409
I'm going to tell my father.

98
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,960
my mother didn’t run away voluntarily.

99
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,480
It was Song Huainan.

100
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,920
It's all because of him.

101
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,780
Bbal-kang is back.

102
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,640
Bbal-kang!

103
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:32,280
Bbal-kang!

104
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,680
Bbal-kang!

105
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,880
What happened?

106
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,480
Who did this?

107
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:44,920
It was Song Huainan.

108
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,000
He killed my mother.

109
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,960
He has no grudge against your mother.

110
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,560
Why did he kill her?

111
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,120
Bbal-kang.

112
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,640
I saw it with my own eyes.

113
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:10,400
he killed my mother with a gun.

114
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,520
That bastard.

115
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,320
Father, you're here.

116
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,559
How dare you come back?

117
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,919
Tell me. Why did you kill Bbal-kang?

118
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,120
That bitch?

119
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:42,559
Because I hate her. She deserves to die.

120
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:44,920
My mother married into the Song family first.

121
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:47,240
But you married that bitch.

122
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:49,000
If it weren't for her, would my mother have died?

123
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,240
What's wrong with killing her?

124
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,000
You bastard!

125
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,840
So that's what you thought.

126
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,800
Do you know

127
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,600
that Bbal-kang was found by your mother?

128
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,240
She knows she doesn't have much time left.

129
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,360
and she trusts Bbal-kang.

130
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,120
take good care of you for her.

131
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:00,880
But you...

132
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,640
did such an ungrateful thing.

133
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,520
Guards!

134
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:06,240
Arrest this unfilial son!

135
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:15,760
I'll take care of the Song family for you.

136
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,400
You...

137
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:17,840
What do you mean?

138
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,440
You're old now.

139
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,200
You should rest at home.

140
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,080
You...

141
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:28,960
Take my father to his room to rest.

142
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,330
Without my permission,

143
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,520
without my permission.

144
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:33,560
Yes.

145
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,080
You unfilial son!

146
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,280
Bastard!
